<div class="index-banner d-flex align-items-center" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586263048715-d2460938153c?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80');">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="banner-text d-flex">
      <h1> <%= @plant.name %> </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container">

  <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="plant-card-image-show-main mb-5 carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>

    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <div class=" d-block plant-card-image-show" style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path @plant.photos.first.key, crop: :fill %>')">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <div class=" d-block plant-card-image-show" style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path @plant.photos.first.key, crop: :fill %>')">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <div class=" d-block plant-card-image-show" style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path @plant.photos.first.key, crop: :fill %>')">
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card-border mb-5">

    <div class="container p-0 d-flex">

      <div>
        <h5 class="mb-4 mr-5">Hi, my name is <%= @plant.name %>!</h5>
        <p class="mb-5 mr-5"><%= @plant.description %>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illum, quam nam et perspiciatis dolorem nobis illo facere qui mollitia est voluptatem aut iste in ab ipsa soluta. Earum, dolorem, doloribus? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Facere eos mollitia sapiente perspiciatis totam, iste, quae voluptates. Tenetur incidunt fuga eum iure, nemo suscipit, excepturi cupiditate officia omnis dolorum dolorem.</p>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
          <div class="mr-4">
            <%= image_tag("https://www.flaticon.com/svg/static/icons/svg/1460/1460537.svg", size: "30") %>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-0 ml-2">
            <p class="mb-0"><%= @plant.category %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="mr-4">
            <%= image_tag("https://www.flaticon.com/svg/static/icons/svg/846/846066.svg", size: "30") %>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-2">
            <p class="mb-0"><%= @plant.price %> EUR</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="booking-card border border-secondary">
        <h5 class="mb-0 mt-2">Add dates for prices</h5>

        <div class="col-auto p-0">
          <label class=“sr-only” for="inlineFormInputGroup"></label>
          <div class="input-group mb-4">
            <div>Move-in</div>
            <div class="input-group-prepend">
              <input type="date" class="form-control" id="inlineFormInputGroup" placeholder="12/10/2017">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="input-group mb-4">
            <div>Move-out</div>
            <div class="input-group-prepend">
              <input type="date" class="form-control" id="inlineFormInputGroup" placeholder="12/10/2017">
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm mt-3" style="width: 100%">Calculate</button>
      </div>
    </div>



  </div>
</div>

<hr>
<%= render 'shared/footer' %>
